 marketers to make quick, simple edits? Most tools are built for pros, and AI videos often feel a bit off. We kept hearing: Why can t I just make a fast explainer or a talking avatar without a studio? </p><p></p><p>That s what we want to change:</p><ul>\n<li><p>Instantly create videos from text prompts</p></li>\n<li><p>Bring blogs, courses, and social posts to life with talking avatars</p></li>\n<li><p>Experiment and storyboard easily not just edit</p></li>\n</ul>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "685070", "name": "Kirill Petrov", "username": "kirill_petrov", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/685070/8e2206cd-1214-44af-a736-3fc775c316a8.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": false, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": {"id": "1072749", "name": "Tila AI", "slug": "tila-ai", "logoUuid": "4a0e31d6-8c60-4bad-875f-51da59e0d401.png", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "__typename": "Product"}, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 25, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 8, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "7", "slug": "general", "subject": {"id": "100", "name": "General", "thumbnailUuid": "85c8f053-f68f-486f-a83b-79bd21080edc.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "689982", "pageViewsCount": 706, "slug": "what-s-the-best-ai-video-generator", "createdAt": "2025-04-20T07:58:52-07:00", "path": "/p/general/what-s-the-best-ai-video-generator", "title": "What's the best AI video generator?", "descriptionPreview": "<p>In the last few days, I have seen many AI tools for creating audio-visual, and even people in my feed shared short movies created by AI (Hollywood will probably cut costs quite a bit in the next few years).</p><p></p><p>What is your experience with AI video generators, and which ones do you find the best? <br>(In terms of which A